Reasoning: The paper discusses the use of Machine Learning and Natural Language Processing algorithms for identifying the programming language of code snippets. This falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) and computational linguistics (cs.CL) sub-categories. The use of a Multinomial Naive Bayes classifier also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper deals with programming languages (cs.PL) and their identification, making this sub-category a likely fit as well.
